          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/51102530-the-real-happiness">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/23100707-jean?shelf=e-book">e-book</a>, 
