        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2894899939" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14070813795861921373">This is a multifaceted story about a young man in search of himself and his faith. The story is well written. The story kept my interest and the pace moved right along. The story is interesting and well worth the read. I chose to read the book because the author is a Goodreads’ author and I want to expand my reading experience.<br/><br/>I read this as an e-book downloaded from Amazon to my Kindle app for my iPad. The book is 351 pages and publishing date is July 4, 2019.<br/></span>

          </span>
        </div>


