        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2899100663" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8491680906051847662">The author added me out-of-the-blue several days ago, and I decided to check out this book of his he’s advertising. It takes no more than a glance to see that he’s harassing people to give him 5 star reviews through emotional manipulation - and then, almost blatantly and without shame, making new accounts to give <i>himself</i> five star reviews. Read the replies of the one star reviews, and then scroll through the five star ones. It’s all there. Absolutely no integrity. I will not be reading this book</span>
  <span id="freeText8491680906051847662" style="display:none">The author added me out-of-the-blue several days ago, and I decided to check out this book of his he’s advertising. It takes no more than a glance to see that he’s harassing people to give him 5 star reviews through emotional manipulation - and then, almost blatantly and without shame, making new accounts to give <i>himself</i> five star reviews. Read the replies of the one star reviews, and then scroll through the five star ones. It’s all there. Absolutely no integrity. I will not be reading this book.</span>
