<span id="freeTextContainer9791597676474339036">The line; to understand it, all one has to do is to close his eyes and look closely, was so appealing in the synopsis that I couldn’t stop myself from reading the book. <br/><br/>The book crafts a very creative series of events explaining the values of an individual’s life. This person holds an exceptional perspective towards the stereotypical societal norms. Another different thing to notice in the book is that, for someone being completely constrained with the usual it seems quite impossible to be uniqu</span>
  <span id="freeText9791597676474339036" style="display:none">The line; to understand it, all one has to do is to close his eyes and look closely, was so appealing in the synopsis that I couldn’t stop myself from reading the book. <br /><br />The book crafts a very creative series of events explaining the values of an individual’s life. This person holds an exceptional perspective towards the stereotypical societal norms. Another different thing to notice in the book is that, for someone being completely constrained with the usual it seems quite impossible to be unique. <br /><br />Hence, the same values are prescribed and integrated into the same storyline through an alternative description. <br /><br />Lastly, the concept of love, friendship and one’s beliefs are profoundly narrated. Fabulous turn of events and beautiful ending. Happy reading to you all.</span>
